title: U S Army NBC F.M 3-7 pdf
description:
NBC-Nuclear Biological-Chemical

    By Order of the Secretary of the Army: GORDON R. SULLIVAN
General, United States Army Chief of Staff
MILTON H. HAMILTON
Administrative Assistant to the
Secretary of the Army
1994

This manual, FM 3-7, is designed as a guide to help the chemical soldier at battalion
level and below in NBC defense. It details the NBC warning and reporting system,
and how to locate, identify, and operate in and around NBC contamination. This
manual is designed to bean easy-to-read, step-by-step manual depicting the manual
method of calculating NBC defense procedures useful for the field soldier.
